This repository contains the public version of the book

    `Introduction to Scientific Programming',

which came out of its namesake course
taught by Victor (with others) for the Texas Advanced Computing Center
to students at The University of Texas at Austin.

This is a source repository for people who want to customize the book.
If you are only interested in the pdf, checkout:

https://web.corral.tacc.utexas.edu/CompEdu/pdf/isp/

which has the book and all lecture slides.
